caption.p: The Theil-Sen (%/year) trend in monthly average ozone levels and the annual SOMO35 and 4 th highest MDA8 human health metrics (A4MDA8) for a suburban site for 1980–2013 in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania (US EPA AQS ID: 421010024–1). The p < 0.05 value was used to determine significance using the Mann-Kendall test. DOI: https://doi.org/10.1525/elementa.279.f11
